                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12667048" author="breed" created="Sun, 25 Jan 2009 06:06:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch allows processing containers to be started up on distributed servers. the system test then spawns servers and clients on the servers to run the tests.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12667898" author="phunt" created="Wed, 28 Jan 2009 01:03:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Found some issues with this. In particular the docs. I&apos;ll  upload a new patch for that (also license issues). But there is still an issue with running the tests. ant is not picking up the system tests. perhaps add the ability to run system tests to the fatjar?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12667900" author="phunt" created="Wed, 28 Jan 2009 01:04:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;add missing licenses to src files and also update the readme to list the steps to run the tests, ben to make some addl changes for running the tests from the command line.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12668574" author="breed" created="Thu, 29 Jan 2009 19:54:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added a way to run the system unit test more easily and fixed a couple of bugs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12669038" author="mahadev" created="Fri, 30 Jan 2009 21:34:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;i removed some @override tags that allowed the code to be compile via java 1.5.0_13 on my mac.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12669076" author="breed" created="Fri, 30 Jan 2009 23:20:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;resynced patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12669104" author="phunt" created="Sat, 31 Jan 2009 00:49:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;fixes a small typo in the patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12669109" author="phunt" created="Sat, 31 Jan 2009 01:04:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed revision 739475.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
